These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: tea, cola
1. the person drinking cola is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |
| Beverage   | cola | tea |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-2::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  mechanic, doctor
1. the mechanic is on the left or right of the doctor##3
2. the doctor is on the right of the mechanic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1     |      2      |
| Job   | mechanic | doctor |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: chess, collecting
1. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is chess##3
2. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |
| Hobby   | collecting | chess |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-4::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: metal, disco
1. the fan of disco is on the left of the fan of metal##1
2. the fan of metal is on the left or right of the fan of disco##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |
| Music-Genre   | disco | metal |

 #################################

 
